@startuml 知识库管理交互时序图

skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam participantFontSize 13
skinparam noteFontSize 11

actor 用户 as User
participant "前端页面" as Frontend
participant "MetadataManager" as MM
participant "TextExtractor" as TE
participant "TextChunker" as TK
participant "VectorStore" as VS

User -> Frontend : 创建知识库并上传文档
Frontend -> MM : register_knowledge_base(name, desc)
MM --> Frontend : 返回 kb_id
Frontend -> TE : extract(file_path)
TE --> Frontend : 返回清洗后纯文本
Frontend -> TK : chunk(text, size, overlap)
TK --> Frontend : 返回分块列表
Frontend -> VS : add_chunks(kb_id, chunks)
VS --> Frontend : 向量化入库完成
Frontend --> User : 展示分块结果与向量详情

@enduml
